## API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Module | Description |
|--------|----------|--------|-------------|
| GET | `/` | — | Health check |
| GET | `/dashboard` | All | Aggregated live stats from all modules |
| POST | `/trainer/log-rep` | 1 | Log reps from Trainer camera |
| GET | `/trainer/history` | 1 | Recent workout sessions |
| GET | `/trainer/workout-stats` | 1 | Total reps, favourite exercise |
| GET | `/trainer/streak` | 4 | Streak + habit history |
| GET | `/trainer/habit-stats` | 4 | Attendance rate, best day/hour |
| POST | `/trainer/log` | 4 | Log daily attendance |
| POST | `/trainer/predict` | 4 | ML skip prediction |
| POST | `/trainer/save-progress-photo` | 1 | Save Cloudinary URL to DB |
| GET | `/trainer/progress-photos/{username}` | 1 | Fetch photo gallery |
| POST | `/dietician/recommend` | 2 | Generate diet plan via RAG + Gemini |
| POST | `/dietician/chat` | 2 | Follow-up diet questions |
| GET | `/equipment/recommend` | 3 | Smart equipment recommendation |
| POST | `/buddy/chat` | 5 | Chat with FitBot |
| POST | `/performance/analyze` | 6 | Biomechanical motion efficiency scoring |
| POST | `/recommender/plan` | 7 | Generate weekly workout plan |
| GET | `/recommender/workout-tips` | 7 | Goal-specific training tips |

Full interactive docs available at `http://localhost:8000/docs`

---

## Module Details

### Module 1 — AI Gym Trainer
- MediaPipe Pose loaded via CDN — avoids Vite bundling issues (`window.Pose`)
- 33 body landmarks detected in real time via webcam
- Joint angles calculated using arctangent formula
- **Exercises:** Left Curl, Right Curl, Squats
- **Posture Check** — 4 real-time checks: shoulder level, head position, spine alignment, head drop — scored out of 100
- Reps logged to `workout_sessions` table every 5 completions
- Progress photos uploaded to Cloudinary, URL stored in `progress_photos` table

### Module 2 — AI Dietician (RAG)
- 15 nutrition documents seeded into ChromaDB on first run
- User query retrieves top 4 relevant docs via vector similarity
- Retrieved context + BMI/BMR/TDEE profile injected into Gemini prompt
- Calculates: Harris-Benedict BMR, TDEE with activity multiplier, goal-adjusted calorie target
- Returns: macro split, full meal plan, grocery list, 3 personalised tips
- Follow-up chat with quick-question chips
- Saves each session to `diet_logs` — personalises repeat visits

### Module 3 — Smart Gym Assistant
- Reads user's entire workout history from SQLite
- Maps top exercises detected to complementary physical gym equipment
- Automatically deduplicates and cleans equipment lists for structured API responses

### Module 4 — Habit Tracker
- Logs: mood (1-5), stress (1-5), planned hour, came/skipped
- Trains **RandomForestClassifier (150 trees)** on full `habit_logs` history
- Falls back to rule-based prediction when fewer than 5 entries exist
- Returns: skip probability, personalised nudge, feature importance breakdown
- Personalised insight: tracks high-stress attendance rate from DB history
- History visualised as bar chart in Dashboard

### Module 5 — Virtual Gym Buddy (FitBot)
- **VADER** detects compound sentiment score (-1 to +1)
- **TextBlob** measures subjectivity (0 to 1)
- Detects 7 struggle types: fatigue, stress, skipping risk, injury, low mood, plateau, academic pressure
- RAG retrieves 3 motivational quotes relevant to message content
- Gemini system prompt changes completely based on detected emotion
- Reads past chat history from `chat_history` table — remembers frequent struggles
- Conversation history maintained per session (last 10 exchanges)
- Name screen on entry — personalised responses using user's name

### Module 6 — Pose-to-Performance Analyzer
- Integrates with MediaPipe form accuracy scores and Rep duration metrics
- Computes non-linear performance efficiency scores out of 100 using NumPy (`np.power`)
- Analyzes Time Under Tension (TUT) and consistency variance for advanced technical insights
- Triggers strict form penalties and dynamic feedback logic

### Module 7 — Gym Recommender
- 22 workout templates across 5 goals and 3 difficulty levels
- User preference encoded as feature vector (level, equipment, target duration, calories)
- **Cosine similarity** ranks all matching workouts — same technique as Netflix/Spotify
- Builds 7-day weekly plan with appropriate rest days
- Weekly split templates: PPL for muscle gain, HIIT/Cardio alternating for weight loss, etc.
- 3 goal-specific tips + 1 level-specific tip returned alongside plan
- Plan count tracked in `recommendations` table

### Interactive Dashboard
- Live stats from all 5 modules in one view
- Animated counters (count up from 0 on load)
- SVG performance rings — attendance %, mood score, reps progress
- Habit bar chart — last 14 days (purple = attended, grey = skipped, height = mood)
- VADER sentiment bar — visualises average compound score
- Module activity feed — highlights from each active module
- Quick navigation links to all 5 modules
- Auto-refreshes every 30 seconds

---

## How the Database Improves the App

| Module | How stored data feeds back |
|--------|---------------------------|
| Habit Tracker | ML trains on ALL `habit_logs` entries — accuracy improves over time |
| Gym Buddy | Reads most frequent struggle from `chat_history` — FitBot remembers patterns |
| Dietician | Detects repeat sessions from `diet_logs` — builds on previous plans |
| Recommender | Tracks plan count from `recommendations` — shows how many times generated |
| Dashboard | Aggregates all 5 tables into live stats |

---
## Known Limitations

- MediaPipe requires good lighting and full body/arm visibility
- Habit ML needs 5+ logged entries to activate (rule-based until then)
- Gemini free tier: 15 requests/minute limit
- SQLite suitable for demo — not for concurrent production use
